      icon: "Py",
      objective: "用 scipy.interpolate.interp1d 从稀疏采样点构造插值函数，再在更密的网格上求值。",
      starterCode: "from scipy import interpolate\nimport numpy as np\n\n# 每隔几小时测一次温度的稀疏采样\nhours = np.array([0, 4, 8, 12, 16, 20, 24])\ntemp  = np.array([12.0, 11.0, 15.0, 22.0, 24.0, 18.0, 13.0])\n\n# TODO: 用 interpolate.interp1d 构造三次样条插值函数, 赋给 f\n#       记得传 kind=\"cubic\"\nf = None\n\n# 想知道每一个整点小时的温度\nfine_hours = np.linspace(0, 24, 25)\n\n# TODO: 用 f 在 fine_hours 上求值, 赋给 fine_temp\nfine_temp = None\n\nprint(fine_temp)\n",
