      starterCode: "import pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\n\nclose = pd.Series(\n    [10, 11, 12, 11, 13, 14, 15, 14, 13, 12, 11, 12, 14, 16, 18],\n    index=pd.date_range('2024-01-01', periods=15, freq='D'),\n    name='close',\n).astype(float)\n\nSHORT, LONG = 3, 5\n\n# TODO: 用 close.rolling(SHORT).mean() 算短期均线 ma_short\n# TODO: 用 close.rolling(LONG).mean() 算长期均线 ma_long\n# ma_short = ...\n# ma_long = ...\n\n# TODO: 短线 > 长线时 position 为 1，否则为 0\n# 提示：np.where(ma_short > ma_long, 1, 0)\n# position = ...\n\nprint(pd.DataFrame({'close': close, 'ma_short': ma_short, 'ma_long': ma_long, 'position': position}))\n",
      hints: ["rolling(N).mean() 是滑动窗口平均：每一天取最近 N 天的均值，前 N-1 天会是 NaN。", "金叉/死叉策略的核心：短线在长线上方代表上升趋势，就持仓（position=1）。", "np.where(条件, 1, 0) 能把布尔条件一次性变成 1/0 的仓位序列。"],
